Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Not too fast now, Angel bunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.89,0:00:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't wanna get a tummy ache.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.43,0:00:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You really should eat more\Nthan that, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not playtime yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.18,0:00:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you wanna run, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...just three more bites.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.73,0:00:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Two more bites?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.19,0:00:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One more bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.73,0:00:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you coughing because there's\Na carrot stuck in your throat?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you need some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that giant cloud\Nof scary black smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.75,0:01:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take that as a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please? Help?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.56,0:01:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's... there's a horrible cloud of smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.59,0:01:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's headed this way and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be such a scaredy-pony. It's just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Future Equestria ball-bouncing record holder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:01:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,246... 247...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.87,0:02:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This calls for a celebration!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... No, Pinkie Pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.79,0:02:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time for celebration.\NThis is a time for panic. For...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna need balloons!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,One for everypony in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's... there's smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.85,0:02:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And... and where there's\Nsmoke, there's fire. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6...\N-...254, 255...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.52,0:02:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,7!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie! Now I have to start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all gonna have to start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In a new village. Because ours is gonna be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Rainbow Dash! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please. This is an emergency.\NI need everypony to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoke is spreading over all of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I've been trying to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.30,0:02:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just received a letter from Princess Celestia\Ninforming me that it is not coming from a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming from a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A... d-d-d-dragon...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the name of all things cinnamon swirled\Nis a full-grown dragon doin' here in Equestria?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,According to Princess Celestia,\Nhe's taking a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,His snoring is what's causing all the smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He should really see a doctor.\NThat doesn't sound healthy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.33,0:03:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least he's not snoring fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we meant to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you what we're meant to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Give 'im a boot. Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to encourage him\Nto take a nap somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia has given us\Nthis mission and we must not fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do, Equestria will be covered in smoke\Nfor the next one hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Talk about getting your beauty sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, everypony.\NI need you to gather supplies quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a long journey ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's meet back here in less than an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, girls! You heard her.\NThe fate of Equestria is in our hoofs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have what it takes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:03:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Much better! Onward!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... let's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, girls. Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm mapping out the fastest route...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...but we've all got to keep a good pace if we\Nexpect to make it up the mountain by nightfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.82,0:04:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,M-m-mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The dragon is in that cave at the very top.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Look pretty cold up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet it is. The higher you go,\Nthe chillier it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing I've brought my scarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooo... Pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. That'll keep you nice and cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... excuse me. Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-I know you're busy, but...\N-Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we could go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-But if I could just have a second...\N-Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we wanna avoid that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, um... I was thinking that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... maybe I should just stay here at Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-Uh-huh.\N-Oh! Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay here and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! You have to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your way with wild animals\Nwill surely come in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and don't worry about your\Nlittle friends in the meadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike's got it covered while you're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know I think he's up to the task. Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want\NFluttershy to come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that pony is afraid of her own shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just gonna slow us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's just a little nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we get going, I'm sure she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.69,0:06:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what it sound like\Nwhen a dragon snores.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... it's so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...high.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it IS a mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna fly up there and check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on now. I think\Nwe should all go up together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:06:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Safety in numbers and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear the only thing that sparkles\Nmore than the dragon's scales...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...are the jewels they use to build their nests.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If I play my cards right, I might be\Nable to convince him to part with a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.38,0:07:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to my cave, Rarity?\NCare for a diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls! This is no laughing matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, you're the expert on wild creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think the dragon will be like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,An invitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooo! I think I have one in my bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It... it's so... so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...steep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it IS a cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You could just... oh, I don't know, fly up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Fluttershy, you can do it.\NFlap those wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,O... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll need this if I'm gonna take her\Naround the mountain another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Around the mountain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's gonna take them forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Twi. We'll be there lickety split.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,WOOHOO! I win again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... That's thirty-five games in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Best of seventy-one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We... made... it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Told you it was gonna take them forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your turn, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's so wide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Fluttershy.\NWe should be much farther along by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You could just leap on over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be afraid of.\NIt's just a hop, skip and a jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.91,0:09:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not very far\Njust move your little rump{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can make it if you try\Nwith a hop, skip and jump{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A hop, skip and jump\Njust move your little rump{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A hop, skip and jump\NA hop, skip and jump{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ahopskipandjump\NAhopskipandjump{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ahopskipandjump!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A hop...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's it!\N-You're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...skip...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I forgot to jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,According to my map, we're\Nentering an avalanche zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The smallest peep could\Ncause a huge rockslide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,An... an ava... ava...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,AVALA...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why a girl always\Npacks extra accessories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please tell me I brought\Na tiara that goes with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we've got bigger problems than making\Nsure our hair bows match our horseshoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.02,0:11:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no big whoop, sugar cube.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! We'll just have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.38,0:11:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...climb over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.88,0:12:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not *your* fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Still think it was a good idea\Nto bring Fluttershy along?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're about to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, you'll use\Nyour wings to clear the smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity and Pinkie Pie...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...you create a diversion to distract\Nthe dragon if things get a little hairy in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack, you're ready with\Nthe apples in case he decides to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But it shouldn't come to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...because Fluttershy will do what\Nshe needs to do to wake him up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...and between the two of us, we should be able\Nto get him to understand why he needs to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everypony ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then. We're going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what is the best way to wake up\Na sleeping dragon without upsetting him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.76,0:13:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Every... second longer that dragon...\Nsleeps is another...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...acre of Equestria that is covered in... smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I... I can't go in the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh great. She's scared of caves now too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared of caves. I'm scared of...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that, sugar cube?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of d...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But Fluttershy. You have a wonderful\Ntalent dealing with all kinds of animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.85,0:14:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because they're not dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! We've seen you walk right up\Nto a horrible manticore like it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because he wasn't a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike is a dragon. You're not scared of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because he's not a huge, gigantic,\Nterrifying, enormous, teeth-gnashing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...sharp-scale-having, horn-wearing,\Nsmoke-snoring, could-eat-a-pony-in-one-bite...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...totally all grown up dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you're so afraid of dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...why didn't you say something\Nbefore we came all the way up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was afraid to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us are scared of that dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost all of us are scared of that dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But we've got a job to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So get in there with Twilight and\Nshow her what you're made of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.19,0:15:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably just doesn't\Nrealize what he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good. You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow me to introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Twilight...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...Sparkle and my friends and I are\Nresidents here in Equestria...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...Ponyville to be exact.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We come here to ask that you find\Nanother spot to take your nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It' just that you seem to be\Ndoing an awful lot of snoring...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...and every time you do, you\Nsend out a terrible cloud of smoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Equestria simply can't survive\Na hundred years in a dark haze.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'll find another place to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for... persuading him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, this situation just\Ncalls for a little "pony charm".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry to interru-hupt...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I couldn't possibly head back home without\Nmentioning what handsome scales you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:17:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And those scales have to be hidden away\Nin some silly cave for a hundred years?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, I think you should skip the snoozing\Nand be out there. Showing them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, I would be more than happy to\Nkeep an eye on your jewels while you're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was this close to getting that diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean... getting rid of that dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... yeah. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, you look ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharing a laugh is a sure-fire way\Nto get someone on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently he doesn't like laughing, heh.\NOr sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We've tried persuasion, charm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...whatever it is Pinkie Pie does...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to stop wasting time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,GET OUT!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,HOW DARE YOU?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen here, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you're big\Ndoesn't mean you get to be a bully.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have huge teeth and sharp scales\Nand snore-smoke and breathe fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...but you do not, I repeat, YOU DO NOT...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:18:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,HURT. MY. FRIENDS!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,BUT THAT RAINBOW ONE KICKED ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.07,0:19:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am very sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're bigger than she is\Nand you should know better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.83,0:19:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You should also know better\Nthan to take a nap...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...where your snoring can become\Na health hazard to other creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,BUT I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you "but I" me, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what do you have to say for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you have to say for yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there. No need to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a bad dragon.\NYou've just made a bad decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go pack your things. You'll just need\Nto find a new place to sleep. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:20:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it! I knew you could do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How does Fluttershy put up\Nwith you furry little things?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.19,0:20:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.71,0:20:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,With pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dear Princess Celestia."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"I am happy to report that the dragon\Nhas departed our fair country..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"...and that it was my good friend Fluttershy,\Nwho convinced him to go."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"This adventure has taught me to\Nnever lose faith in your friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"They can be an amazing source of strength..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.73,0:20:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"...and can help you overcome\Neven your greatest fears."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Always your faithful student,\NTwilight Sparkle."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight! You gotta come see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just five away from a new pony record.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.03,0:20:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,247... 248...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:20:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you laughing?!\NThat awful dragon is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, you scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... uh, you broke my concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Rainbow Dash.\NNot everypony can be as brave as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.30,0:21:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Synced by Nathan2000\Nhttp://mlp.wikia.com/wiki/User:Nathan2000
